vote.title: Authorize the second of two, one-year renewal options to the service price agreement with Catholic Charities of Dallas, Inc. for supportive services for seniors for the Housing Office of Homeless Solutions for the period of October 1, 2023 through September 30, 2024 - Not to exceed $250,000.00 - Financing: General Fund
